  "description": "A transcranial magnetic stimulation combined with electroencephalography (TMS-EEG) dataset consisting of single-pulse open-loop stimulation recordings. This dataset is mirrored from OpenNeuro (ds002094) and provides neurophysiological measurements of brain responses to focal magnetic stimulation, suitable for investigating cortical excitability, connectivity, and TMS-induced neural dynamics. Original dataset creators: [Authors from OpenNeuro ds002094].",
